[[File:God of Saiha.png|thumb|right|170px|Saiha Shin]] '''Saiha Shin''' (歳破神, さいはしん) is one of the {{ill|Eight Guardian Deities|ja|八将神|1=Eight Directional Deities|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eight Guardian Deities|13=User:Immanuelle/Eight Directional Deities|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eight Guardian Deities|13=User:Immanuelle/Eight Directional Deities|qq=}} in [[:en:Onmyōdō|Onmyōdō]]. In certain calendars, it may also be written as "さいは" (Saiha). The {{ill|honji|ja|本地|1=Honji suijaku|2=ja|3=本地垂迹|lt=Honji|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/honji|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/honji|13=User:Immanuelle/Honji suijaku|qq=}} of this deity is identified as [[:en:Hebo|Hebo (Chinese deity)]], the Great Water God.
Saiha Shin is regarded as the essence of [[:en:Saturn|Saturn]] (鎮星). This deity resides in the direction opposite that of {{ill|Taisai Shin (Tai Sui)|ja|太歳神|1=Taisai Shin|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taisai Shin (Tai Sui)|13=User:Immanuelle/Taisai Shin|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taisai Shin (Tai Sui)|13=User:Immanuelle/Taisai Shin|qq=}}, another of the Eight Guardian Deities. However, it is said that Saiha Shin is often attacked and overpowered by Taisai Shin, which makes Saiha Shin a malevolent deity. Note that in [[:en:Flying Star Feng Shui|Nine Star Ki]], the directional term '''Saiha''' (歳破) is a distinct concept from the deity Saiha Shin.
Saiha Shin embodies the characteristics of {{ill|Earth (Wu Xing)|ja|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|zh|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|lt=Earth (土)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|zh|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|lt=Earth (土)|lt=Earth (土)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth (Wu Xing)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth (Wu Xing)|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth (wuxing)|zh|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|lt=Earth (土)|qq=}}. It is considered inauspicious to perform actions like {{ill|earthworks|ja|動土|qq=